data.description: NEW ROOF IS IN THE WORKS! This luxury New Orleans style townhouse in popular Lafittes Landing boasts exquisite features and elegant custom woodwork throughout. The living room welcomes you with beautiful stained and scored concrete floors, complemented by a cozy gas fireplace. The space is adorned with gorgeous crown moldings, showcasing the attention to detail in the home's design.The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring custom wood cabinets, granite tile countertops, and a gas cooktop. The abundance of counter space makes meal preparation a breeze. Additionally, the kitchen offers a convenient power strip under the counter, fleur de lis cabinet pulls, and functional front shutters, adding a touch of sophistication and charm. The master suite, located on the bottom floor, is a private sanctuary. The master bath boasts double vanities, a separate shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Adding to the luxurious ambiance, a lovely chandelier hangs over the master tub. An elegant wood and iron staircase leads to the upper floor, where two bedrooms and a full bath are located. These rooms provide ample space for family or guests, offering comfort and privacy. The townhouse also offers two private patio areas one covered and one open providing a serene and secluded atmosphere for relaxation and entertaining. Storage is not an issue in this townhouse. There is attic access on the second floor and an all-floored area over the garage, providing plenty of space to store belongings. Overall, this luxury townhouse in Lafittes Landing combines the charm of New Orleans style with modern amenities and ample storage, creating an ideal home for those seeking elegance and comfort. HOUSE IS ABOUT TO GET A NEW ROOF!
